A lobbying campaign service company targetting the EU on behalf of corporate customers.  Publications from BKSH suggests that BKSH is largely envisaging service for multinational corporations with deeply entrenched patent departments and is readily using lies and deceptive rhetoric of such prospective customers, possibly even before having been employed by them.  

== News & Chronology ==

 * 2004-11-08 EU [:Bksh041108En: BKSH: Software Patent Directive Falling Apart] -- says verbosely that the Council's directive allows patents on automobile brakes etc but not on plain business software and that "industry" needs it  
